      The system shall declare the second run complete when the robot pose is within a configured position and orientation tolerance of the target cell center.
    </Content>
  </Requirement>

  <Requirement ID="LL-RELIAB-5.1.1">
    <Type>NFR</Type>
    <Name>No Contact With Walls</Name>
    <Relationships>
      <Refines>HL-RELIAB-5.1</Refines>
