    <Content>
      The system shall select proximity and hard-stop thresholds and corresponding motion commands such that, under nominal sensor and actuator behavior, the robot chassis shall remain at least a configured minimum nonzero distance away from any wall.
    </Content>
  </Requirement>

  <Requirement ID="LL-RELIAB-5.1.2">
