    <Content>
      The system shall implement an exploration state machine with, at minimum, the following states: IDLE, EXPLORE, RETURN_TO_START, and SECOND_RUN, and shall transition between these states based on exploration progress and completion or abort of path execution as defined by the path execution completion and abort conditions.
    </Content>
  </Requirement>

  <Requirement ID="LL-EXPL-1.2.0.1">
